<plot>Three Native American friends are on the road to a powwow, but each is on his own personal journey. Grappling with grief, Dean must honor his mother's memory. Tired of being the screw-up, Joey must learn to believe in himself. And always the hothead, Mark must face his own prejudices. They unwillingly meet up with a wayward party girl, and get stranded on a dirt road in Kansas. While searching for the next town, they discover surprising and sometimes painful truths about themselves. When tragedy strikes, Dean is forced to confront his personal demons -- and follow his heart home to the powwow world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?125727</url></doc>
